.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, almond-milk, cola
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, collecting, fishing, gardening
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rowing, soccer, swimming
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's sport is rowing##1
2. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
3. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
4. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
5. the person who's hobby is baking is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person who's sport is soccer##2
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person drinking fanta and the person drinking almond-milk##2
7. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the right of the person who's hobby is fishing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |   3    |     4      |
| Beverage    | almond-milk | hot-chocolate  | fanta | cola      |
| Hobby   | fishing  | gardening  | baking | collecting |
| Sport   | swimming | ice-hockey | rowing | soccer     |

