.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-7::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, papaya, pepper, pomegranate
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: drama, epic, mystery, spy
4 different pets are kept: frog, snake, chinchilla, mouse
1. the owner of the mouse is the person watching epic movies##1
2. the owner of the chinchilla is the person watching drama movies##1
3. the person watching mystery movies is on the far left##1
4. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
5. the person eating pepper is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
6. the person eating papaya is between the person watching epic movies and the person watching mystery movies##2
7. the person eating pomegranate is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |    4     |
| Food          | pepper  | papaya    | pomegranate | lettuce  |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | spy       | epic        | drama    |
| Pet         | snake | frog | mouse  | chinchilla |

