3. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
4. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
5. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |      4      |
