2. the person who growsdaffodil is the person eating eggplant##1
3. the fan of house is on the left of the person eating mango##1
4. the person who growspoppy is the person eating mango##1
5. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
6. the person who growspoppy is on the far right##1
7. the person who growsdaffodil is between the fan of salsa and the person who growsorchid##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Food          | tomato  | eggplant    | pepper | mango       |
