.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-10::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, orange, pepper, pomegranate
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, collecting, dancing, gardening
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, tea, fanta, hot-chocolate
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left##1
2. the person eating pepper is on the far left##1
3. the person eating orange is between the person eating lettuce and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
4. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person eating pomegranate##1
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
8. the person drinking milk is the person eating pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Food          | pepper      | pomegranate | orange | lettuce |
| Hobby         | gardening   | collecting  | baking | dancing |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | milk   | tea | fanta |

