.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-11::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, garlic, raspberry, strawberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, puzzles, reading
There are 4 different nationalities: japanese, brazilian, russian, mexican
1. the person eating garlic is on the right of the person eating eggplant##1
2. the russian is the person eating garlic##1
3. the japanese is between the person who's hobby is camping and the person who's hobby is puzzles##2
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the japanese and the person eating strawberry##2
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is the mexican##1
6. the person who's hobby is board-games is the brazilian##1
7. the person who's hobby is reading is the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3     |     4      |
| Food    | strawberry  | raspberry | eggplant | garlic     |
| Hobby   | board-games | puzzles   | reading  | camping    |
| Nationality     | brazilian        | mexican       | japanese      | russian |

