The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, gardening, sudoku, traveling
4 different pets are kept: bird, goat, pony, turtle
1. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person watching thriller movies##1
3. the person watching animation movies is between the person watching thriller movies and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left##1
5. the person watching animation movies is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
6. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
7. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | thriller     | animation | fantasy       |
| Hobby      | sudoku  | traveling | card-games  | gardening |
| Pet        | turtle  | goat      | pony        | bird      |

