.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, mirinda, soy-milk
4 different games are played: billiard, domino, snooker, canasta
There are 4 different nationalities: german, indian, italian, mexican
1. the person playing billiard is the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking mirinda and the indian##2
3. the person drinking mirinda is the person playing domino##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is between the person playing snooker and the mexican##2
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the german is between the italian and the person playing canasta##2
7. the person playing billiard is the mexican##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | mirinda | cola   | soy-milk |
| Game   | billiard  | domino    | snooker   | canasta     |
| Nationality   | mexican  | italian | german | indian   |

