.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-19::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  dancer, freelancer, journalist, librarian
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, milk, lemonade, sprite
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, scooter, subway, taxi
1. the person drinking milk is on the right of the journalist##1
2. the person drinking sprite is the person driving the roller##1
3. the dancer is on the far left##1
4. the person driving the subway is the librarian##1
5. the person drinking water is the person driving the subway##1
6. the person driving the taxi is between the person drinking milk and the person driving the subway##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | dancer        | librarian  | journalist | freelancer   |
| Beverage       | sprite | water | lemonade    | milk |
| Transport   | roller        | subway     | taxi       | scooter      |

